transcript.text: Creating custom art or logos with Designer Studio is easy and enjoyable.
Start by clicking on Art Layout where you'll find 2 sections, Custom and My Library.
To design your art or logo from scratch, head to the My Library section and click on Create Artwork.
Choose from a variety of clip art or shapes, add creative and relevant text, and customize the style or colors to match your vision.
Once your design is complete, be sure to save your artwork in the Customs section.
You'll start by selecting your preferred colors and entering the text for your design, such as Black Friday Sale.
Click Continue to explore a variety of system generated design options.
Personalize your chosen design further by selecting icons from a wide range of available choices.
Once you've finalized your design, click the Save icon to give your artwork a name and apply it to the product canvas.
You can then customize it further by modifying colors, text, styles, and fonts.
When you're happy with your design, simply proceed to place your order.
If you want to revisit or edit your saved designs, you can access them under the My Library section or in the My Saved Designs option from the My Account menu.
With just a few simple steps, Designer Studio empowers you to create, refine and perfect your custom art or logos effortlessly.
